**R1 Findings**

- F001: `resolved-correct`。`enabled_modules` / `capabilities` / `available_tools` / `profile` 已在 try 前预初始化，[ai.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/ai.py#L111) 到 [ai.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/ai.py#L114)；fallback 后构造 `ToolContext` 时不再依赖未赋值局部变量，[ai.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/ai.py#L157)。

- F002: `resolved-correct`。`_SessionState` 已持有 `history`，[ai.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/ai.py#L37)；HTTP 入口把历史传给 `AgentLoop.run(..., history=...)`，[ai.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/ai.py#L191)；结束后回写 `loop.get_history()`，[ai.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/ai.py#L202)。`AgentLoop` 也已接收、注入并导出历史，[agent_loop.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/ai/agent_loop.py#L64)、[agent_loop.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/ai/agent_loop.py#L72)、[agent_loop.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/ai/agent_loop.py#L244)。我额外做了同一 `session_id` 的双请求对抗验证，第二次请求确实带上了第一轮 user/assistant 历史。

